--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Jonathan" <jhogan@r...> wrote:
> {Grimlock}
> 
>     Grimlock stomped down the corridor, his large feet clanking 
loudly on
> the metallic floor of the corridor. At each door he stopped a 
moment raised
> his black fist and pounded three solid times on the portal before 
speaking,
> "Me Grimlock say speak up any bot! Me looking for bots still 
working! Me
> Grimlock say speak up!"
> 
>     At each silent room he moved on, hammering on each door in 
turn, growing
> more bored with each door as he looked down at Daytripper, "Me 
Grimlock no
> like playing hide and seek. Me say we go to mess hall. Me Grimlock 
hungry,
> me say bots come find us there!"

"wow I didn't know you where on board" Kenzo said when he spotted 
Grimlock in the halls "Are you looking for something?" he asked.
